|NPCID|69664| |LVL|Level 92| |ABIL|139010,139004,139003,136738| |NDIS|97268,94221,94222,92426| |ST|As a melee you must kite the (npc:69806) he spawns while DPSing him or you're going to have a bad day. They melee for about 110k on leather and you're not going to be able to heal yourself back up from it while you have the 99% reduced healing taken debuff he puts on you. <br/><br/>If you're low from taking too many hits from a (npc:69806) his (spell:139004) attack will finish you off. Make sure you run away to drop your healing debuff to top yourself up if you need it. The spirits are slow-moving and can also be snared so you shouldn't have any issues continuing to DPS the boss while kiting them.<br/><br/>Found in (map:928) (35.10, 62.50, 928, "(npc:69664)")|
