|NPCID|117275| |NAME|Stitches| |LVL|Rank 4.4| |ABIL|236154,236146| |ST|(npc:117275) moves around in a puddle of goo. Standing in the puddle gives you a stacking debuff (spell:236154) and you can reset this if you move out; if the stack reaches ten (10) you instantly die. If you move out of the aura (npc:117275) will hook you back in with (spell:236146); this stacks for every hook and lasts for two (2) minutes, making it slower and slower to move out and reset the stacks.|	
|NPCID|114945| |NAME|Wes| |LVL|Rank 5.1| |ABIL|231710,231662,229152| |ST|The brawl against (npc:114945) and (npc:114944) takes place on a "stage" with a fiery curtain and large jukeboxes at the one end, which shoots (spell:231710) across the arena. Each jukebox is offset, so you can dodge in and out to avoid getting damaged, unless you are rooted by (spell:229152) from (npc:114945). The jukeboxes shoot (spell:231662) as well, which you need to jump over to avoid -- failing to do so will prove fatal quite fast, so be careful of (spell:229152) during this. You will also fight a couple of (npc:115639)s that are cheering the music on.|	
