|NPCID|67591| |NAME|Millie Watt| |LVL|Rank 6.2| |ABIL|133363,133362,133306,133361| |ST|(npc:67591) is a gnome engineer with a large gun. She casts (spell:133363), which you must avoid, unless she's channeling her cast (spell:133362), which turns you into a chicken. Make use of the electric zone to disrupt the polymorph and zap you back into shape, leaving behind the debuff (spell:133306). She also has a channeled (spell:133361) that you can disrupt with knockbacks or stuns.|	
