|NPCID|117146| |NAME|Mazhareen| |LVL|Rumble| |ABIL|134534| |ST|(npc:117146), formerly a Rank 3 brawl in Warlords of Draenor, resembles the striped cat (npc:32517) found in Sholazar Basin. This is not a very melee friendly fight. (npc:117146) does increased damage the lower her health drops. Below 25% you can easily get one-shot. Your best approach is to keep (npc:117146) stunned or feared for the last portion of the fight. Where this is not possible, save all defensive and offensive cooldowns for the second half of the fight, and burn her down before she decides to chew your face off!|	
